<h2 id="toc8"><span>CHRISTMAS LOOT:</span></h2>
<p>I raise a mug of matcha to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chrisakapiefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1578588); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1578588&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608430599" alt="ChrisAKAPiefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1578588)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chrisakapiefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1578588); return false;">ChrisAKAPiefish</a></span> who drew this interpretation of my own SCP-2794, for <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-1998814">The 5th Annual X-Mas Art Exchange</a> &gt;w&gt;</p>
